That may be true, but riven has a lot of counters. 
For example you can pick a lane dominant champion like {{champion:122}} {{champion:80}} .
You can also pick a champion that's a tank and farm from a distance (non interactive) {{champion:14}} 
You can also take a champion that can roam really well {{champion:133}} 
The other option is to pick skill match ups {{champion:39}} {{champion:114}}
